snippet.title: Dil (1990) (HD & Eng Subs) - Aamir Khan | Madhuri Dixit | Anupam Kher - Hit Bollywood Romantic Movie
snippet.description:
Movie Starts At: 03:41

Best Scene from the Movie: 1:01:28

Dil is the story of Raja and Madhu whose innocent love story is wrecked by the egos of their prejudiced fathers. Raja is the son of Hazariprasad, a scrap vendor while Madhu is the daughter of Mr. Mehra, a wealthy industrialist. Raja's father pretends to be a rich businessman before Madhu's dad but his lies are nailed during Raja and Madhu's engagement ceremony causing him embarrassment. Watch how Raja and Madhu's undying love for each other forces their respective fathers to bury the hatchet and accept their marriage. 

YOR – 1990
Star Cast - Aamir Khan, Madhuri Dixit, Anupam Kher, Saeed Jaffrey, Deven Verma, Adi Irani
Director – Indra Kumar
Producer – Indra Kumar, Ashok Thakeria
Music Director – Anand - Milind
Cinematographer – Baba Azmi
Stroy - Rajiv Kaul, Praful Parekh 
Screenplay - Rajiv Kaul, Praful Parekh 
Dialogues - Kamlesh Pandey
